<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f0f0f0;
            margin: 0;
            background-image: url('https://i.pinimg.com/originals/08/96/51/0896511df173f914d1ee6bd45bcfac82.jpg');
            padding: 0;
        }
        .navbar {
            background-color: #a300d9;
            color: #fff;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 10px 20px;
        }
        .navbar a {
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin: 0 10px;
        }
        .navbar a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #ECECEC90;
            border-radius: 5px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }
        .hero {
            background-color: #9fec25;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .btn {
            background-color: #fff;
            color: #0074d9;
            border: none;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        .btn:hover {
            background-color: #eee;
        }
        .grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
            gap: 20px;
        }
        .card {
            background-color: #0cd4f3;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 5px;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .card img {
            max-width: 100%;
            height: auto;
        }
        .dropdown {
            position: relative;
            display: inline-block;
        }
        .dropdown-content {
            display: none;
            position: absolute;
            background-color: #050505;
            color: #f4f1f1; 
            min-width: 160px;
            box-shadow: 0px 8px 16px 0px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
            z-index: 1;
        }
        .dropdown:hover .dropdown-content {
            display: block;
            color: black;
        }
        .dropdown button {
            background-color: transparent;
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
            outline: none;
        }
    </style>
    <title>About Me</title>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="navbar">
        <a href="/">Lego Collection</a>
        <a class="active" href="/about">About</a>
    </div>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="hero">
            <h1>About Me</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="grid">
            <div class="card">
                <img src="https://www.unigreet.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Srushti-WhatsApp-dp-1024x1024.jpg" alt="Srushti Patel">
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <p>I am Srushti Patel. I love to play Garba (Indian Gujarati Folk Dance). I am enrolled in the Computer Programming Course in Seneca College studying in 3 Semester with my subjects as WEB322, OOP345, SYD211, NAT161, DBS311.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
